review 1:
Good food, great taste, perfect place for people who love quiet dining... little bit romantic if i could say...
the place might be "isolated" and not many people stop here, but the food is much much much cheaper and taste better than you find in Jimbaran. we ordered 3 very huge fish, 4 coconuts, 3 portion of tofu, 4 portion of rice, and 1 large kangkung cah. with total price of IDR 2xx.000 (i forgot the exact number, sorry). meaning one person only pays around 50.000 IDR and booooi lemme tell you ... our stomach almost exploded!
